---
const rows = [
  {
    scattered: "Campaigns live across chats, docs, and meetings",
    system: "Campaigns live in one organized system",
  },
  {
    scattered: "Every asset starts from scratch",
    system: "The system remembers the business before the next draft starts",
  },
  {
    scattered: "Approvals get buried and repeated",
    system: "Decisions become approval memory for future work",
  },
  {
    scattered: "Lead lists get researched once, then forgotten",
    system: "Opportunities connect to follow-up and next steps",
  },
  {
    scattered: "Content quality depends on who has time that week",
    system: "Campaigns keep moving with a clear weekly rhythm",
  },
  {
    scattered: "The team keeps asking what comes next",
    system: "Markethink brings the next move back for review",
  },
];
---

<section class="comparison-section" id="comparison">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="comparison-shell animate-fade-up">
      <div class="comparison-header">
        <p class="subtitle">WHY IT MATTERS</p>
        <h2>Most teams do not need another app. They need the work to connect.</h2>
        <p>
          Markethink is the operating layer between strategy, content, approvals, leads, web updates, and follow-up. The value is not one more place to log in. The value is marketing that keeps moving because the system remembers the business.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="comparison-table" role="table" aria-label="Scattered marketing compared with Markethink">
        <div class="comparison-row comparison-row-head" role="row">
          <div role="columnheader">Scattered marketing</div>
          <div role="columnheader">Markethink system</div>
        </div>
        {rows.map((row) => (
          <div class="comparison-row" role="row">
            <div role="cell">
              <span class="status-dot status-dot-muted" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              {row.scattered}
            </div>
            <div role="cell">
              <span class="status-dot status-dot-active" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              {row.system}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .comparison-section {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    background: #f5f5f1;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .comparison-shell {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.8fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .comparison-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 7.5rem;
  }

  .comparison-header .subtitle {
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.5);
  }

  .comparison-header h2 {
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .comparison-header p {
    max-width: 31rem;
    color: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.62);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .comparison-table {
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-medium);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.56);
  }

  .comparison-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.08);
  }

  .comparison-row:first-child {
    border-top: 0;
  }

  .comparison-row > div {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    min-height: 4.75rem;
    padding: 1.15rem 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.64);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .comparison-row > div + div {
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.08);
    background: rgba(237, 244, 234, 0.78);
    color: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.84);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .comparison-row-head > div {
    min-height: auto;
    background: #0f1213;
    color: #f5f5f1;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.11em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .comparison-row-head > div + div {
    background: #0f1213;
    color: #69d254;
  }

  .status-dot {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 0.62rem;
    height: 0.62rem;
    margin-top: 0.42rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .status-dot-muted {
    background: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.18);
  }

  .status-dot-active {
    background: #69d254;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.35rem rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.14);
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .comparison-shell {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .comparison-header {
      position: static;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .comparison-section {
      padding: 4.5rem 0;
    }

    .comparison-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .comparison-row > div + div {
      border-left: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.08);
    }
  }
</style>
